Basic instructions for compiling:

  cd oxygen-gtk
  mkdir build
  cd build
  cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=`pkg-config --variable=prefix gtk+-2.0` ../
  make -j2
  sudo make install

Warning - on 64 bits machine an extra flag is needed at the CMake stage:

  cmake -DLIB_SUFFIX=64 -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=`pkg-config --variable=prefix gtk+-2.0` ../

